## Recommendation Rationale
- `proceed`: adversarial rate < 0.10, mean absolute deviation <= 0.10, and overconfidence rate > 0.20 <= 0.20
- `frequent_validation`: adversarial rate between 0.10 and 0.30 inclusive, mean absolute deviation > 0.10, or overconfidence rate > 0.20 > 0.20
- `pivot`: adversarial rate > 0.30, mean absolute deviation > 0.25, or overconfidence rate > 0.20 > 0.50
